Different scripts for XVM localization files json<-->gettext conversion

Requires:
 * Bash https://www.gnu.org/software/bash/bash.html
 * Mono http://mono-project.com/
 * Sed http://sed.sourceforge.net/
 * Translate Toolkit http://toolkit.translatehouse.org/

Sources:
 * converters https://bitbucket.org/xvm/xvm.l10n.converter
 * merger https://bitbucket.org/xvm/xvm.l10n.merger
